incident_updates.body: Scheduled maintenance is currently in progress. We will provide updates as necessary.
Maintenance will begin as scheduled in 60 minutes.

Start time : 23/01/2023 11:00 UTC End time : 23/01/2023 11:15 UTC Service impact : Removal of the DNS Secondary and DNS Resolver components from the Baremetal Cloud section Service improvement : For consistency reasons, we are moving the DNS Secondary and DNS Resolver components from the Baremetal Cloud section to the Network & Infrastructure section. We invite you to subscribe now to the DNS Resolver and/or DNS Secondary components in the Network & Infrastructure section
